<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/50225824-secrets-in-the-dark"><img alt="Secrets in the Dark (Black Winter, #2)" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1577244838l/50225824._SX98_SY160_.jpg" />
